data.description: Tastefully renovated gem, nestled quaintly along the Ocean County Golf Course at Atlantis. This 3-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom townhouse is an exceptional find, offering the perfect combination of modern comforts plus natural aesthetic beauty. Step inside, you're greeted by an open floor plan that seamlessly flows. Enjoy the tranquil and picturesque backdrop, with lots of privacy. This townhouse is 100% move-in ready. The comprehensive renovation of the townhome includes: New carpeting, Fresh paint, New HVAC, Updated flooring, new granite countertops and sinks in the kitchen, Modern vanities, New lighting fixtures, New refrigerator, New sliding glass door leading to the enclosed screened-in porch, perfect for enjoying the outdoors without the pests. This one is a must-see and won't last!
